channel.title: !Pictures! Tynthox [317] Delta (Now with site/more pictures)
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/2aj5o3p.jpg[/img][/center] [center]Click [url=http://tynthox.tk]here[/url] to follow updates and the project.[/center]
Hello again, My old development team didn't attract any post more than likely due to the lack of information for the server itself, but only ideas forming upon themselves.
The programmer will be able to code a 317 delta source, the source is Gods Corruption, I will be probably mostly recoding all areas, adding more minigames, fixing bugs/glitches, and more little things that don't matter at the moment. I will have images up shortly.
The server is a Eco/Pk, customs are added, such as bandos warspear, d claws, statius helm, working vestas sword, dragon plate body. Pking will be simple with some different zone for those who wish to fight their own level variation, 1v1, or ?v?. Minigames will be classical with the hope of some customs, such as a minigame I myself created in which you fight 1 normal npc in order to achieve money or gold(its classic but fun) more elaborate minigames such as Last Man standing, Clan wars, and others will hopefully be added in the length of the server's uptime.
Small List of Features(theres more but heres a few) Working Orbs Exp Lock Customs God Wars Pest Control Fully working Barrows Cleaned home(name says it, took away objects that, well don't matter making more room) & More!
I've been playing rsps and Rs for 5 years so I know what I am doing, I will code and make graphic design.
A programmer will need to know basic coding and some elaborate skills.
Hoster will need to be 24/7 until VPS can be afforded.
Programmer will receive co-owner, Hoster Head Admin (any problems with these rankings leave it in your application)
Web Designer will be required to design a website/forums
Video Editor will be required to edit and upload videos to YouTube
Application Name: Age: Skype: MSN: Spot: Experience: Proof of work:
Spots Open: Programmer: 2/3 Hoster: 0/1 Web Designer: 1/1 Video Editor: 1/1
[IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/5arv9z.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/2d6wmcp.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/jq3os2.jpg[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/qAXQL.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/ToMeP.png[/img] More compact home, aka cleaned home.
